%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20moved%20from%20London%20to%20NYC.%26nbsp%3BHere%20are%207%20things%20that%20surprised%20me%20when%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20UK%20for%20the%20first%20time.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Central%20London%20(Left)%20and%20New%20York%20City%20(Right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65983ca3ec62ab5daf811d3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22956%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECentral%20London%20(Left)%20and%20New%20York%20City%20(Right).%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELast%20year%2C%20I%20left%20my%20home%20in%20London%20to%20move%20to%20NYC.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20are%20often%20compared%2C%20but%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20NYC%20and%20London%20are%20pretty%20different.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGetting%20to%20the%20airport%20is%20easier%20in%20London%2C%20but%20the%20subway%20has%20a%20number%20of%20perks%20the%20tube%20lacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsurprising-things-about-moving-to-new-york-from-london-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20from%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20New%20York%20City%20last%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20my%20official%20move%20date%2C%20I%20assured%20friends%20and%20family%20that%20it%20wouldn't%20take%20me%20long%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmoving-to-nyc-from-london-mistakes-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20feel%20at%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20of%20how%20similar%20the%20two%20places%20are%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0both%20are%20huge%20cities%20that%20feel%20cosmopolitan%2C%20international%2C%20and%20fast-paced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsurprising-things-moving-to-us-from-uk-after-4-years-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewent%20back%20to%20the%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20visit%20family%20that%20I%20noticed%20seven%20surprising%20things%20that%20made%20me%20realize%20the%20two%20cities%20have%20less%20in%20common%20than%20I%20previously%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETraveling%20into%20central%20London%20from%20Heathrow%20is%20much%20more%20straightforward%20than%20getting%20into%20Manhattan%20from%20JFK.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22London's%20Heathrow%20Airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659860f8ec62ab5daf813396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELondon's%20Heathrow%20Airport.%3Cp%3EHollie%20Adams%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20fly%20into%20London%20Heathrow%20when%20I%20go%20back%20to%20the%20UK.%20From%20the%20airport%20to%20the%20city%20center%2C%20travelers%20can%20choose%20between%20taking%20a%20taxi%2C%20the%20London%20Underground%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20tube)%2C%20or%20the%20Heathrow%20Express%2C%20a%20high-frequency%20rail%20link%20between%20the%20airport%20and%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20there%20are%20no%20direct%20public%20transportation%20routes%20from%20where%20I%20live%20in%20Manhattan%20to%20JFK%2C%20which%20is%20the%20airport%20I%20usually%20fly%20out%20of.%20That%20means%20I'm%20usually%20left%20with%20paying%20around%20%24100%20for%20a%20taxi%20or%20taking%20a%20tediously%20long%20journey%20on%20a%20bus%2C%20subway%2C%20and%20the%20AirTrain%20that%20can%20last%20up%20to%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20barely%20noticed%20London's%20big%20red%20buses%20when%20I%20lived%20there.%20After%20months%20in%20NYC%2C%20they%20felt%20like%20a%20novelty.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20typical%20bus%20in%20London%20(Left)%20and%20in%20New%20York%20City%20(Right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659862651c5c7b8c9a0e7e9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20typical%20bus%20in%20London%20(Left)%20and%20in%20New%20York%20City%20(Right).%3Cp%3EMarcoGovel%2FGetty%20Images%2C%20Michael%20Lee%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20pay%20much%20attention%20to%20London's%20signature%20red%20double-decker%20buses%20when%20I%20lived%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20living%20in%20NYC%2C%20where%20every%20bus%20is%20white%20and%20blue%20and%20only%20has%20one%20floor%2C%20I%20gained%20a%20new%20appreciation%20for%20the%20ones%20in%20my%20home%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20moving%20to%20the%20US%2C%20I%20rarely%20went%20out%20of%20my%20way%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20top%20deck%20of%20a%20London%20bus.%20However%2C%20during%20my%20first%20visit%20back%2C%20I%20sat%20up%20top%20every%20time%20I%20took%20the%20bus.%20Unlike%20NYC%20buses%2C%20they%20really%20are%20the%20best%20way%20to%20soak%20up%20the%20city%20views%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20sit%20at%20the%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20used%20to%20love%20a%20leisurely%20stroll%20in%20London.%20But%20when%20I%20went%20back%20to%20visit%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20myself%20longing%20to%20be%20around%20fast-paced%20New%20Yorkers.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Crowds%20of%20people%20walking%20through%20the%20intersection%20of%2023rd%20Street%20and%20Fifth%20Avenue%20in%20Midtown%20Manhattan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659863521c5c7b8c9a0e7f80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECrowds%20of%20people%20walking%20through%20the%20intersection%20of%2023rd%20Street%20and%20Fifth%20Avenue%20in%20Midtown%20Manhattan.%3Cp%3Edeberarr%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20walking%2C%20New%20Yorkers%20are%20known%20for%20being%20fast%20and%20furious.%20It's%20a%20stereotype%2C%20but%20one%20that%20rings%20true%20from%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20London%2C%20I%20quickly%20realized%20that%20I'd%20become%20accustomed%20to%20the%20quicker%20walking%20pace%20most%20New%20Yorkers%20have%20and%20actually%20preferred%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20catching%20up%20with%20friends%20and%20going%20for%20walks%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20having%20to%20slow%20down%20to%20their%20pace.%20The%20worst%2C%20however%2C%20was%20visiting%20crowded%20areas%20like%20Oxford%20Circus%20where%20I%20grew%20super%20frustrated%20at%20how%20slow%20people%20were%20walking%20in%20front%20of%20me%20on%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELondoners%20will%20travel%2045%20minutes%20across%20the%20city%20with%20zero%20complaints.%20The%20same%20cannot%20be%20said%20for%20New%20Yorkers%2C%20in%20my%20experience.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20London%20skyline.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6598646b6979d7371820f46b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22915%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20London%20skyline.%3Cp%3EKarl%20Hendon%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20weeks%20after%20I%20moved%20to%20NYC%2C%20I%20met%20someone%20who%20warned%20me%20not%20to%20move%20to%20Brooklyn%20because%20it%20would%20be%20impossible%20to%20maintain%20friendships%20with%20people%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20this%20was%20a%20joke%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20I%20soon%20discovered%20that%20New%20Yorkers%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20actually%20consider%20anywhere%20that%20isn't%20walkable%20or%20takes%20longer%20than%2030%20minutes%20to%20get%20to%20by%20subway%20too%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20in%20London%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20rediscover%20that%20spending%2045%20minutes%20on%20public%20transportation%20or%20in%20a%20taxi%20is%20pretty%20standard%20for%20going%20anywhere%20in%20the%20city.%20Whether%20it%20be%20drinks%2C%20dinner%2C%20or%20friends'%20places%2C%20taking%20into%20account%20that%20the%20journey%20will%20likely%20be%20close%20to%20an%20hour%20is%20custom%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20thought%20I'd%20miss%20the%20tube%2C%20but%20I%20have%20to%20admit%20the%20subway%20has%20its%20perks.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20London%20tube.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e4aff3cc84b4dfa0003b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222781%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20London%20tube.%3Cp%3ETim%20Grist%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20always%20have%20a%20soft%20spot%20for%20the%20tube%2C%20but%20after%20moving%20to%20NYC%2C%20I%20have%20to%20admit%20the%20subway%20has%20it%20beat%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0for%20several%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fabric%20seat%20covers%20on%20the%20tube%2C%20which%20are%20often%20discolored%20from%20how%20old%20they%20are%20and%20how%20many%20people%20have%20sat%20in%20them%20over%20the%20years%2C%20now%20feel%20super%20unhygienic%20compared%20to%20the%20plastic%20seats%20on%20the%20subway.%20Subway%20cars%20are%20also%20air-conditioned%2C%20a%20feature%20that%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20tube%20lines%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20shocked%20me%20the%20most%20after%20returning%20to%20London%20was%20the%20price%20of%20the%20tube.%20In%20NYC%2C%20the%20fare%20to%20go%20anywhere%20in%20the%20city%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnew.mta.info%2Fguides%2Friding-the-subway%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapped%20at%20%242.90%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20London%2C%20a%20single%20fare%20ride%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftfl.gov.uk%2Fcampaign%2Fnew-fares%3Fintcmp%3D34454%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eduring%20peak%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20costs%20%C2%A32.80%2C%20about%20%243.57%2C%20which%20increases%20if%20you%20travel%20outside%20certain%20zones%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENYC%20never%20sleeps%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20London%20does.%20After%20a%20few%20months%20in%20the%20Big%20Apple%2C%20I%20was%20grateful%20for%20the%20rest.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22925%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NYC%20nightlife%20is%20a%2024%20hour%20affair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c5ef21c5c7b8c9a0ef8cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22694%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENYC%20nightlife%20is%20a%2024%20hour%20affair.%3Cp%3ESiegfried%20Layda%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20NYC%2C%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20people%20I%20met%20raved%20about%20was%20that%20you%20can%20do%20pretty%20much%20anything%20you%20want%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20time%20or%20day%20of%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20having%20a%20full%20three-course%20dinner%20at%202%20a.m.%20or%20going%20to%20karaoke%20at%203%20a.m.%20is%20always%20fun%2C%20it%20can%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20your%20energy%20and%2C%20sadly%2C%20your%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20returning%20to%20London%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0where%20pubs%20close%20at%2011%20p.m.%2C%20restaurants%20at%20midnight%2C%20and%20bars%20at%202%20a.m.%20%E2%80%94%20felt%20like%20such%20a%20relief%20after%20months%20in%20NYC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20was%20also%20nice%20to%20grab%20a%20drink%20and%20dinner%20in%20London%20without%20worrying%20about%20how%20much%20to%20tip.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tipping%20culture%20in%20the%20US%20doesn't%20exist%20in%20the%20UK.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c5f45ec62ab5daf81af31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETipping%20culture%20in%20the%20US%20doesn't%20exist%20in%20the%20UK.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Cary%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20London%20perk%20I'd%20forgotten%20about%20after%20moving%20to%20NYC%20is%20t