0changed%20their%20exterior%20marquee%20signs%20to%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BDave's%20NOT%20Chicken.%26quot%3B%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dave's%20Not%20Chicken%20sign%20in%20Santa%20Ana%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c86646979d73718218021%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20chain%20changed%20its%20marquee%20to%20%26quot%3BDave's%20Not%20Chicken%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20Santa%20Ana%2C%20California%20restaurant.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDave's%20Hot%20Chicken%20was%20founded%20as%20a%20pop-up%20restaurant%20in%20East%20Hollywood%20in%202017.%20It%20became%20an%20overnight%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20had%20the%20foresight%20three%20years%20ago%20to%20trademark%20%26quot%3BDave's%20Not%20Chicken%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20began%20to%20consider%20non-meat%20options%20for%20the%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20chain's%20culinary%20team%20couldn't%20find%20%26quot%3Bany%20product%20that%20delivered%20the%20same%20craveability%20as%20our%20chicken%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chain%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArman%20Oganesyan%2C%20one%20of%20Dave's%20co-founders%20and%20chief%20brand%20officer%2C%20tried%20fried%20cauliflower%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20and%20put%20it%20on%20the%20brand's%20radar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerious%20testing%20occurred%20after%20Chick-fil-A%20rolled%20out%20its%20cauliflower%20sandwich%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeeing%20Chick-fil-A's%20test%20further%20validated%20that%20this%20could%20be%20a%20viable%20option%2C%20so%20long%20as%20we%20could%20nail%20the%20flavor%20profile%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chain%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20it%20took%20several%20weeks%20in%20the%20test%20kitchen%20to%20create%20a%20meat%20alternative%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20so%20tasty%2C%20even%20our%20most%20dedicated%20hot%20chicken%20lo