dress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethousands%20of%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Britain%20caught%20up%20in%20what%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20called%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20biggest%20miscarriages%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarely%20a%20week%20after%20ITV%20started%20airing%20%26quot%3BMr%20Bates%20vs%20the%20Post%20Office%2C%26quot%3B%20Rishi%20Sunak%20told%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20that%20the%20government%20was%20introducing%20legislation%20to%20quash%20the%20convictions%20of%20more%20than%20700%20subpostmasters.%20They%20run%20small%20post%20offices%2C%20often%20in%20little%20communities%20where%20everyone%20knows%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scandal%20dates%20back%20more%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20century%2C%20when%20the%20Post%20Office%20brought%20in%20a%20computer%20system%20at%20huge%20expense%20to%20modernize%20its%20operations.%20That%20system%2C%20supplied%20by%20Japan's%20Fujitsu%2C%20appeared%20to%20show%20that%20many%20subpostmasters%20were%20stealing%20money%20%E2%80%93%20but%20they%20were%20not.%20It%20was%20the%20Horizon%20system%20that%20was%20faulty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20were%20jailed%2C%20or%20were%20left%20bankrupt%20by%20repaying%20debts%20they%20never%20incurred%20or%20having%20their%20businesses%20taken%20away%20from%20them.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.standard.co.uk%2Flifestyle%2Fpost-office-heartbreaking-stories-subpostmasters-b1130880.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESeema%20Misra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20convicted%20of%20stealing%20%C2%A374%2C000%20(about%20%2495%2C000)%20and%20sentenced%20to%2015%20months%20for%20theft%20and%20false%20accounting%2C%20said%20she%20would%20have%20killed%20herself%20had%20she%20not%20been%20pregnant%20with%20her%20second%20child%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20Huxham%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20July%202020%20after%20being%20jailed%20for%20eight%20months%20over%20a%20%C2%A316%2C000%20shortfall%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20his%20marriage.%3Cbr%3EMartin%20Griffiths%2C%2059%2C%20jumped%20in%20front%20of%20a%20bus%20in%202013%20after%20being%20falsely%20accused%20of%20theft%20at%20his%20post%20office%20branch%20in%20Ellesmere%20Port%2C%20near%20Liverpool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20had%20marriages%20destroyed%2C%20were%20ostracized%20by%20their%20communities%C2%A0and%20ruined%20financially.%20Julian%20Wilson%2C%20for%20one%2C%20died%20before%20being%20able%20to%20clear%20his%20name.%20Each%20case%20is%20shocking%20in%20its%20own%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Village%20Shop%20and%20Post%20Office%20in%20South%20Warnborough%2C%20Hampshire%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a038a36979d73718228cbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJo%20Hamilton%2C%20who%20ran%20the%20Village%20Shop%20and%20Post%20Office%20in%20South%20Warnborough%2C%20Hampshire%2C%20was%20wrongly%20convicted%20of%20theft%20in%20the%20Post%20Office%20Horizon%20scandal.%3Cp%3EAdrian%20Dennis%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJournalists%20have%20been%20covering%20the%20problems%20with%20Horizon%20for%20at%20least%2015%20years%20ago.%20Outlets%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.computerweekly.com%2Ffeature%2FPost-Office-Horizon-scandal-explained-everything-you-need-to-know%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EComputer%20Weekly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Private%20Eye%20and%20public%20broadcaster%20the%20BBC%20covered%20the%20story%20extensively%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0but%20it%20wasn't%20until%20the%20four-part%20drama%20starring%20Toby%20Jones%20(who's%20appeared%20in%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BHunger%20Games%26quot%3B%20films)%20that%20millions%20of%20people%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20injustice%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20untold%20pain%20and%20suffering%20inflicted%20on%20the%20subpostmasters%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221205%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Toby%20Jones%20as%20Alan%20Bates%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a0345cdcdb354a9856cf68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22717%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EToby%20Jones%20as%20Alan%20Bates%20in%20the%20ITV%20drama.%3Cp%3EITV%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20program%20focused%20on%20Alan%20Bates%2C%20who%20along%20with%20his%20partner%20invested%20in%20a%20post%20office%20store%20in%20Wales%20in%201998.%20A%20number%20of%20financial%20discrepancies%20were%20identified%20by%20the%20computer%20system%2C%20and%20when%20he%20refused%20to%20repay%20one%20sum%2C%20the%20Post%20Office%20terminated%20his%20contract%2C%20wiping%20out%20their%20%C2%A360%2C000%20investment%20and%20destroying%20their%20livelihood.%20For%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20Bates%20has%20campaigned%20for%20justice%20for%20hundreds%20of%20people%20like%20him.%20He%20wasn't%20prosecuted%2C%20but%20many%20others%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fbusiness%2F2024%2Fjan%2F08%2Fa-first-class-expose-of-the-post-office-scandal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%20to%20The%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20newspaper%20from%20John%20Beer%20of%20Farnham%2C%20Surrey%20sums%20up%20the%20reaction%20of%20many%20people%3A%20%26quot%3BWith%20increasing%20incredulity%20and%20rage%2C%20I%20viewed%20as%20it%20revealed%20what%20lengths%20some%20senior%20executives%20and%20boards%20will%20go%20to%20protect%20their%20companies%20even%20when%20they%20know%20the%20lives%20of%20so%20many%20good%20and%20honest%20people%20are%20being%20ruined%20or%20terminated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20anger%20galvanized%20ministers%20into%20taking%20incredibly%20swift%20action%20by%20drafting%20a%20new%20law%20to%20clear%20the%20names%20of%20all%20those%20convicted%20%E2%80%94%20although%20cynics%20argue%20that%20a%20looming%20general%20election%20later%20this%20year%20also%20helped%20to%20focus%20minds.%20The%20blanket%20acquittal%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20first%20time%20that%20parliament%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20overturn%20the%20verdict%20of%20courts%20of%20law%2C%20The%20Guardian%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20convictions%20had%20already%20been%20overturned%2C%20most%20had%20not%2C%20and%20a%20government%20inquiry%20into%20the%20scandal%20is%20still%20taking%20evidence%20and%20won't%20report%20until%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20number%20of%20questions%20remain%20unanswered.%20Why%20did%20the%20Post%20Office%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fresearchbriefings.files.parliament.uk%2Fdocuments%2FCBP-7550%2FCBP-7550.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eowned%20by%20the%20government%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202012%20%E2%80%93%20continue%20to%20prosecute%20people%20when%20there%20were%20doubts%20about%20the%20software%3F%20And%20why%20did%20the%20government%20keep%20awarding%20contracts%20worth%20almost%20%C2%A35%20billion%20(%246.4%20billion)%20to%20Fujitsu%20even%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F5119c5a8-d49a-4588-b024-f4d620df7f29%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECourt%20of%20Appeal%20ruled%20in%20December%202019%20that%20its%20software%20was%20at%20fault%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20issue%20of%20whether%20taxpayers%20should%20be%20expected%20to%20foot%20the%20compensation%20bill%20of%20%C2%A3600%2C000%20(%24763%2C000)%20for%20each%20wrongful%20conviction.%20That%20sounds%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20but%20campaigners%20say%20it%20only%20covers%20loss%20of%20earnings%20rather%20than%20include%20damages%20for%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20government%20minister%2C%20Kevin%20Hollinrake%2C%20said%20Fujitsu%20would%20have%20to%20cover%20some%20of%20the%20bill%20if%20it%20was%20found%20%26quot%3Bculpable%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20public%20inquiry.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F5119c5a8-d49a-4588-b024-f4d620df7f29%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFujitsu%20apologized%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20postmasters'%20%26quot%3Bsuffering%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20didn't%20comment%20further%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20respect%20for%20the%20inquiry%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Financial%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conduct%20of%20Post%20Office%20managers%20is%20also%20under%20renewed%20scrutiny.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-67884743%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%20News%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20company%20lied%20and%20made%20threats%20before%20it%20broadcast%20an%20interview%20in%202015%20with%20a%20whistleblower%20who%20revealed%20that%20figures%20on%20the%20Horizon%20system%20could%20be%20changed%20without%20users'%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itv.com%2Fpresscentre%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-12%2FITV%2520Mr%2520Bates%2520vs%2520the%2520Post%2520Office%2520Press%2520Pack.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGwyneth%20Hughes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20wrote%20the%20drama%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20despite%20their%20pain%20and%20suffering%2C%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20Post%20Office%20scandal%20%26quot%3Bmanage%20to%20be%20funny%20and%20warm%20and%20welcoming%20even%20after%2025%20years%20of%20their%20ordeal.%20These%20were%20ordinary%20British%20people%2C%20living%20ordinary%20British%20lives%2C%20until%20suddenly%20they%20weren't%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuddenly%20they%20were%20dubbed%20thieves%20and%20villains%2C%20trapped%20in%20a%20nightmare%20of%20false%20accusation%20and%20public%20humiliation.%20Innocent%20people%2C%20pillars%20of%20their%20communities%2C%20and%20the%20worst%20of%20it%20is%20that%20each%20of%20them%20was%20told%20they%20were%20the%20only%20one%20having%20problems%20with%20the%20Horizon%20computer%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20more%20than%20a%20million%20people%20signed%20a%20petition%20calling%20on%20Paula%20Vennells%2C%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20the%20Post%20Office%2C%20to%20be%20stripped%20of%20a%20public%20honor%20called%20a%20CBE%20given%20to%20her%20in%202019%20for%20services%20to%20the%20organization%2C%20and%20to%20charity.%20This%20week%20the%20former%20Anglican%20priest%20decided%20to%20voluntarily%20return%20the%20honor%20and%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Btruly%20sorry%20for%20the%20devastation%20caused%20to%20the%20sub-postmasters%20and%20their%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlan%20Bates%20had%20refused%20a%20similar%20honor%20while%20Vennells%20still%20held%20hers%2C%20but%20that%20could%20soon%20change.%20Sunak's%20spokesman%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bhard%20to%20think%20of%20someone%20more%20deserving%20than%20him%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20could%20be%20in%20line%20for%20a%20knighthood%20%E2%80%94%20Britain's%20highest%20honor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alan%20Bates%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a0327943bb77284b9c5906%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlan%20Bates%20has%20waged%20his%20campaign%20for%20subpostmasters%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%3Cp%3EHouse%20of%20Commons%2FPA%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20network%20TV%20has%20been%20forecast%20many%20times%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20quite%20dead%20yet.%20That%20may%20be%20only%20because%20advertisers%20still%20find%20it%20the%20best%20way%20to%20reach%20mass%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20it's%20highly%20likely%20that%20if%20a%20streaming%20platform%20or%20even%20a%20pay-TV%20channel%20had%20shown%20the%20drama%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20have%20had%20anything%20like%20the%20same%20impact%20%E2%80%94%20if%20only%20because%20far%20fewer%20people%20would've%20seen%20it.%20The%20program%20and%20an%20accompanying%20documentary%20have%20been%20seen%20by%20almost%2015%20million%20people%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itv.com%2Fpresscentre%2Fmedia-releases%2Fmr-bates-vs-post-office-2024s-most-watched-programme%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20ITV%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20Strong%2C%20the%20director%2C%20told%20BBC%20News%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20astonishing%20%E2%80%94%20we%20thought%20we'd%20hopefully%20raise%20awareness%20and%20get%20the%20story%20of%20the%20victims%20to%20a%20wider%20audience%2C%20but%20no%20one%20ever%20thought%20we'd%20get%20this%20sort%20of%20reaction%20and%20response%20%E2%80%A6%20it's%20mind-blowing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolly%20Hill%2C%20ITV's%20head%20of%20drama%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itv.com%2Fpresscentre%2Fmedia-releases%2Fmr-bates-vs-post-office-2024s-most-watched-programme%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20commissioned%20this%20drama%20because%20it%20was%20a%20story%20that%20demanded%20to%20be%20told.%20Like%20everyone%20watching%20the%20show%2C%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20what%20had%20happened.%20We%20all%20just%20wanted%20the%20drama%20to%20help%20get%20that%20story%20heard%20by%20as%20many%20people%20as%20we%20could.%20ITV%20is%20proud%20to%20have%20told%20this%20story%20and%20to%20support%20the%20subpostmasters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Bates%20vs%20the%20Post%20Office%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20is%20available%20in%20the%20UK%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itv.com%2Fwatch%2Fmr-bates-vs-the-post-office%2F10a0469%2F10a0469a0001%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EITVX%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20A%20US%20broadcaster%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20confirmed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmr-bates-itv-drama-post-office-horizon-scandal-wrongful-convictions-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider