ece%20of%20clothing%20purchased%20online%20in%20a%20post%20office%20and%20possibly%20return%20it%20immediately%3A%20La%20Poste%20is%20experimenting%20with%20fitting%20rooms%20in%20a%20few%20agencies%20in%20France%2C%20upsetting%20certain%20traders%20who%20point%20to%20%26quot%3Bserious%20risks%26quot%3B%20for%20%26quot%3Blocal%20shops%26quot%3B.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a13bf46979d7371822c1f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20changing%20room%20in%20a%20La%20Poste%20branch%20in%20Paris%20lets%20people%20try%20on%20their%20online%20purchases.%3Cp%3EAlain%20Jocard%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFrance's%20post%20office%20is%20trialing%20in-store%20changing%20rooms%20to%20make%20online%20shopping%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bright%20yellow%20booths%20are%20designed%20to%20look%20like%20French%20post%20boxes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20retailers%20are%20concerned%20about%20losing%20even%20more%20customers%20to%20online%20rivals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFrance%20likes%20to%20do%20some%20things%20differently%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0and%20its%20post%20office%20is%20no%20different.%20It's%20testing%20out%20an%20idea%20that%20could%20make%20buying%20clothes%20online%20a%20whole%20lot%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShoppers%20who%20get%20their%20purchases%20sent%20to%20certain%20La%20Poste%20branches%20will%20have%20the%20option%20of%20opening%20their%20parcels%20and%20trying%20on%20their%20new%20clothes%20in%20a%20bright%20yellow%20changing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20some%20items%20aren't%20quite%20right%2C%20all%20they'll%20have%20to%20do%20is%20put%20them%20back%20in%20the%20parcel%20and%20take%20it%20to%20the%20counter%2C%20eliminating%20another%20trip%20to%20the%20post%20office%20to%20send%20the%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesigned%20to%20look%20like%20French%20mailboxes%2C%20the%20changing%20rooms%20are%20being%20trialed%20in%20four%20post%20office%20branches%3A%20two%20in%20Paris%2C%20one%20in%20Lannion%2C%20and%20another%20in%20La%20Rochelle%2C%20French%20magazine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.capital.fr%2Fconso%2Fles-commercants-redoutent-la-concurrence-des-cabines-dessayage-de-la-poste-1490281%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECapital%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20mirrored%20booth%2C%20customers%20can%20place%20their%20belongings%20and%20parcels%20on%20a%20chair%20or%20shelf%20while%20they%20try%20their%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paris%20Changing%20booth%20post%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a13d7143bb77284b9c9275%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20mirrored%20booth%20has%20a%20chair%20and%20shelf%20inside%20for%20customers%20to%20place%20packages%20and%20belongings%20while%20they%20try%20on%20their%20goods.%20%3Cp%3EALAIN%20JOCARD%20%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20they%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20after%20seeing%20how%20many%20customers%20pick%20up%20packages%20only%20to%20return%20them%20a%20few%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shopify.com%2Fuk%2Fenterprise%2Fecommerce-returns%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShopify%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20average%20return%20rate%20for%20online%20purchases%20is%20between%2020%25%20and%2030%25.%20There's%20been%20an%20increase%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20when%20customers%20became%20more%20comfortable%20ordering%20items%20like%20clothing%20on%20the%20web.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20is%20to%20simplify%20the%20lives%20of%20our%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20La%20Poste%20said%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Fjan%2F10%2Ffrench-post-office-opens-changing-room-for-online-shoppers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BCheck%20it%20out%20on%20the%20premises%20and%2C%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20poor%20fit%20or%20a%20change%20of%20mind%2C%20send%20it%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20helps%20people%20avoid%20making%20pointless%20trips%20back%20and%20forth%20and%20save%20time%2C%20it's%20practical%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20customer%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20still%20preferred%20buying%20clothes%20in%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELa%20Poste%20also%20hopes%20the%20experiment%20will%20bring%20more%20people%20into%20its%20branches%2C%20which%20has%20dropped%20as%20sending%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-us-postal-carriers-want-you-to-know%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook.com%26utm_campaign%3Dsf-bi-main%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ViCUoJR7_AncI-7z0qvk_Tkanj3JqncxKpk7OHkWDmj26NXptgURWw3g%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletters%3C%2Fa%3E%20becomes%20less%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225414%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chaning%20room%20Paris%20Post%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a13d116979d7371822c245%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223610%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECustomers%20can%20pick%20up%20parcels%2C%20try%20on%20items%2C%20and%20then%20send%20them%20back%20immediately%20if%20desired.%3Cp%3EALAIN%20JOCARD%20%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20might%20relish%20the%20option%2C%20some%20retailers%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20potential%20impact%20on%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20Retailers%20Association%2C%20which%20represents%20around%20450%2C000%20small%20shops%2C%20said%20La%20Poste's%20changing%20rooms%20trial%20is%20%26quot%3Bcausing%20deep%20displeasure%20among%20small%20independent%20retailers%20and%20poses%20serious%20risks%20to%20the%20vibrancy%20of%20local%20economies%20if%20it%20is%20rolled%20out%20nationally%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22htt