2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20cracked%20on%20and%20tried%20their%20best%20-%20nevertheless%20it%20ultimately%20does%20play%20a%20role%20in%20motivation%20when%20you%20can't%20see%20or%20hear%20that%20support%20base%20around%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20World%20Cup%20campaign%20was%20as%20usual%20marked%20by%20high-level%20off-field%20turbulence%2C%20including%20news%20about%20dressing%20room%20discord%20and%20leaked%20WhatsApp%20conversations%20of%20then%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Arthur%20said%20all%20those%20outside%20commotions%20never%20really%20affected%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20outside%20noise%20with%20Pakistan%20is%20incredible%2C%20you%20just%20have%20to%20check%20your%20Twitter%20feed%20to%20see%20so%20many%20fires%20that%20are%20ignited%20out%20there%2C%20that%20have%20absolutely%20no%20truth%20attached%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20end%20up%20-%20and%20I%20found%20this%20out%20the%20first%20time%20-%20you're%20just%20constantly%20extinguishing%20those%20fires%20and%20chasing%20your%20tail.%20What%20we%20knew%20within%20our%20team%20was%20our%20game%20plan%2C%20and%20the%20defined%20roles%20that%20the%20players%20had%2C%20and%20we%20cracked%20on%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20unequivocally%20no%20massive%20disagreements%20with%20the%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20Arthur%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArthur%2C%20who%20guided%20Pakistan%20to%202017%20Champions%20Trophy%20title%2C%20defended%20his%20decision%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Pakistan%20team%20as%20director%20while%20holding%20on%20to%20his%20job%20with%20English%20county%20Derbyshire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20African%20said%20he%20found%20the%20remarks%20about%20him%20being%20an%20online%20coach%20by%20former%20Pakistan%20players%20to%20be%20unbelievably%20ignorant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnybody%20who%20knows%20me%20will%20also%20know%20that%20I%20will%20not%20commit%20100%20per%20cent%20if%20I%20can't%20do%20it.%20With%20Pakistan%20I%20was%20never%20an%20'online%20coach'%20as%20I%20put%20together%20the%20coaching%20staff%2C%20I%20was%20in%20constant%20contact%20with%20them%20every%20single%20day%20and%20knew%20exactly%20what%20was%20going%20on%20within%20the%20team.%26quot%3B%20Arthur%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20he%20only%20accepted%20the%20job%20second%20time%20with%20Pakistan%20cricket%20because%20of%20his%20great%20relationship%20with%20former%20PCB%20Chairman%20Najam%20Sethi%20who%20hired%20him%20in%20April%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20trust%20Najam%20Sethi%20implicitly.%20We%20have%20a%20very%20good%20relationship%2C%20and%20I%20went%20in%20to%20try%20and%20help%20him%20because%20I%20owe%20him%20a%20lot.%20He's%20the%20one%20who%20gave%20me%20my%20opportunity%20to%20return%20to%20international%20cricket%20after%20I%20had%20been%20sacked%20by%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20I%20built%20up%20a%20good%20relationship.%20One%20of%20the%20reasons%20I%20returned%20was%20to%20specifically%20work%20with%20Najam%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20detailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArthur%20also%20advised%20the%20PCB%20to%20have%20a%20system%20where%20players%20start%20trusting%20the%20structure%20and%20believing%20in%20the%20selection%20process%20and%20play%20for%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20constant%20change%20and%20instability%2C%20players%20go%20into%20self-protection%20mode%2C%20and%20they%20end%20up%20playing%20for%20themselves%2C%20just%20thinking%20about%20the%20next%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20frustrating%20to%20witness%20that%20because%20players%20aren't%20given%20a%20proper%20chance%2C%20there's%20no%20honest%20communication%20and%20they%20know%20things%20are%20always%20going%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705138560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ftolk1aq8_mickey-arthur_625x300_12_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fhostile-environment-in-ahmedabad-ex-pakistan-team-director-mickey-arthur-describes-cricket-world-cup-match-vs-india-4855216%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Pakistan%20team%20director%20admitted%20that%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20India%20at%20Ahmedabad%20was%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20moments%20during%20his%20stint%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20Named%20Chairperson%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20Convenor%20of%20INDIA%20Bloc%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13150404%2Fimage-1736.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcongress-mallikarjun-kharge-india-bloc-chief-9107816%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Opposition-led%20INDIA%20alliance%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%2C%20citing%20sources.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20convenor%2C%20reportedly%20said%20that%20he%20would%20accept%20the%20role%20only%20if%20all%20parties%20reached%20a%20consensus%2C%20sources%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20during%20a%20virtual%20meeting%20attended%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%2014%20Opposition%20parties%20constituting%20the%20bloc.%20The%20agenda%20of%20the%20meeting%20was%20to%20discuss%20seat-sharing%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20S