-no-surprises-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20To%20Lead%20Opposition%20Bloc%20INDIA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20intense%20deliberations%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20been%20chosen%20for%20the%20chairperson%20of%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%2C%20sources%20said.%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20yet%20to%20make%20an%20official%20announcement.%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20another%20contender%20for%20the%20top%20post%2C%20but%20in%20today's%20meeting%20he%20said%20that%20someone%20from%20Congress%20should%20assume%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20or%20'Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance'%20is%20a%20group%20of%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress.%20The%20parties%20have%20come%20together%20to%20take%20on%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20which%20is%20led%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20and%20prevent%20it%20from%20winning%20a%20third%20straight%20term%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20representatives%20from%20all%20parties%2C%20except%20for%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20leaders%20attending%20the%20meet%20stressed%20on%20the%20importance%20to%20ensure%20unity%20at%20the%20national%20level%20and%20not%20allow%20state-level%20rifts%20to%20disturb%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20choosing%20a%20chairperson%20is%20only%20one%20facet%20of%20the%20many%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20They%20still%20have%20to%20tackle%20the%20issue%20of%20seat-sharing%20between%20all%20the%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20a%20forgiving%20mood%20given%20the%20state%20Congress's%20refusal%20to%20share%20any%20seats%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20State%20party%20chief%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20refused%20to%20honour%20the%20central%20leadership's%20commitment%20for%20six%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ripples%20were%20very%20public.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20swipes%20at%20the%20Congress%20were%20followed%20by%20the%20party's%20crushing%20defeat%20in%20the%20three%20heartland%20states%20and%20the%20sacking%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%20from%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20discussion%20with%20AAP%20is%20also%20proving%20contentious.%20While%20the%20party%20wants%204%20seats%20in%20Delhi%20and%20seven%20seats%20in%20Punjab%2C%20AAP%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20comply.%20In%20both%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20wants%20the%20bigger%20share%20of%20seats.%20AAP%20also%20wants%20to%20contest%20in%20Goa%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Gujarat%2C%20sources%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705137660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fgn0gr1a8_mallikarjun-kharge-pti_625x300_22_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-leader-mallikarjun-kharge-named-india-bloc-chief-4854804%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20intense%20deliberations%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20been%20chosen%20for%20the%20chairperson%20of%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-leader-mallikarjun-kharge-named-india-bloc-chief-4854804%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-leader-mallikarjun-kharge-named-india-bloc-chief-4854804%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-leader-mallikarjun-kharge-named-india-bloc-chief-4854804%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22titl