%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eover-eating%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20treats%20by%20pairing%20them%20with%20something%20nutrient-dense%20but%20lower%20calorie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we're%20hungry%20and%20reach%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnacking-wrong-study-healthy-dietitian-healthy-snack-swaps-2023-12%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esnack%20foods%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20ultra-processed%20and%20high%20in%20sugar%20and%20fat%20but%20low%20in%20nutrients%2C%20registered%20dietitian%20Alison%20Clark%2C%20said.%20This%20means%20you're%20getting%20almost%20no%20nutrients%20while%20consuming%20a%20lot%20of%20calories%20and%20won't%20feel%20full%20for%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESnack%20foods%20also%20tend%20to%20be%20what's%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-research-explains-why-cant-stop-eating-chips-ice-cream-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eultra-palatable%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20therefore%20easier%20to%20overeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20goal%20is%20weight%20loss%2C%20such%20treats%20can%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20sticking%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalories-macros-protein-fat-weight-loss-expert-advice-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecalorie%20deficit%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20burning%20more%20calories%20than%20you%20consume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEat%20treats%20alongside%20complex%20carbs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20try%20eating%20treats%20in%20small%20quantities%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ealongside%20a%20complex%20carbohydrate%2C%20such%20as%20wholegrain%20crackers%2C%20and%20some%20fiber%2C%20such%20as%20a%20banana%20or%20apple%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EClark%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20often%20recommends%20her%20clients%20eat%20wholewheat%20cracker%20bread%20with%20cookie%20spread%2C%20the%20spread%20being%20the%20treat%2C%20and%20mashed%20banana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20options%20to%20prevent%20overeating%20snacks%20include%20pairing%20a%20few%20chocolate%20squares%20with%20low-fat%20Greek%20yogurt%20and%20strawberries.%20Or%20having%20a%20sensible%20serving%20of%20chips%20with%20chopped-up%20veggies%20and%20hummus.%20While%20a%20chocolate%20square%20contains%2050%20to%2060%20calories%20on%20average%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20cup%20of%20strawberries%20and%20low-fat%20yogurt%20contains%20around%2050.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20pairings%20allow%20a%20person%20to%20eat%20more%20overall%20but%20feel%20fuller%20at%20the%20end%20thanks%20to%20the%20fiber%20and%20protein%2C%20while%20getting%20more%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hack%20follows%20the%20same%20principle%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-nutrition-reporters-love-8020-rule-for-healthy-diet-2021-4%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%2080%2F20%20rule%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20promotes%20eating%20a%20health-conscious%20diet%20that%20aligns%20with%20your%20nutrition%20goals%2080%25%20of%20the%20time%20while%20being%20more%20relaxed%20for%20the%20other%2020%25.%20This%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20stick%20to%20health%20goals%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20makes%20good%20use%20of%20what%20are%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-volume-low-calorie-meals-snacks-fat-loss-dietitian-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehigh-volume%20foods%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20strawberries%2C%20which%20take%20up%20more%20space%20on%20our%20plates%20and%20stomachs%2C%20meaning%20we%20feel%20satiated%20with%20fewer%20calories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20deprive%20yourself%20because%20you%20know%20as%20well%20as%20I%20do%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20say%20'I'm%20not%20going%20to%20eat%20chocolate%2C'%20you%20want%20it%2010%20times%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%