%2F%2Fukhrultimes.com%2Fbethel-high-school-management-committee-condemns-torturing-of-one-of-its-teachers-at-moreh%2F%5C%22%3Ewere%20allegedly%20subjected%20to%20severe%20beatings%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20abandoned%20in%20the%20jungle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20they%20are%20recovering%20in%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Moreh%20Private%20Schools%20Association%2C%20condemning%20the%20attack%20on%20Holkholal%20Mate%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeter%20was%20brutally%20tortured%20by%20police%20commandos%20on%20the%20night%20of%2030%20December.%E2%80%9D%20Attempts%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20Peter%20have%20been%20unsuccessful%2C%20as%20he%20is%20not%20in%20a%20condition%20to%20speak.%20Images%20received%20from%20a%20source%20show%20extensive%20injuries%20all%20over%20his%20body.%20Besides%20teaching%2C%20Peter%20also%20serves%20as%20the%20secretary%20of%20youth%20at%20St.%20George%20Catholic%20Church%2C%20Moreh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20involving%20Lamminthang%20Lupho%20and%20Jangkholen%20Lupho%20occurred%20on%20January%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20concern%20over%20the%20worsening%20situation%2C%20Kuki%20Students%E2%80%99%20Organisation%20(KSO)%20leader%20and%20an%20advocate%20in%20Moreh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20no%20longer%20trust%20the%20police.%20Members%20of%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20are%20using%20police%20uniforms%20to%20roam%20around%20freely%20and%20pick%20up%20our%20men%20in%20the%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20written%20complaint%20submitted%20by%20Peter%E2%80%99s%20uncle%20to%20the%20Moreh%20police%20station%2C%20Peter%20was%20arrested%20by%20police%20CDO%20personnel%20when%20he%20was%20returning%20home.%20He%20was%20allegedly%20tortured%20throughout%20the%20night%20in%20the%20Police%20IB%2FCDO%20complex.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20threatened%20him%20not%20to%20inform%20the%20matter%20to%20AR%2C%20GR%2C%20BSF%2C%20and%20CSO%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Peter%20told%20me%20they%20were%20members%20of%20Arambai.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArambai%20Tenggol%2C%20Meitei%20Leepun%2C%20and%20Kuki%20Militants%20are%20groups%20that%20both%20communities%20have%20accused%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20members%20from%20the%20other%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmanipur-2-editors-arrested-in-8-days-over-reports-on-law-and-order-in-moreh%5C%22%3EManipur%3A%202%20Editors%20Arrested%20in%208%20Days%20Over%20Reports%20on%20Law%20and%20Order%20in%20Moreh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Kuki%20men%20shoot%20Meiteis%20looking%20For%20wood%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur%2Ffour-meitei-woodcutters-allegedly-killed-by-armed-kuki-men-in-manipur-hunt-on-for-killers-2845123%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFour%2520wood%2520collectors%252C%2520belonging%2520to%2Cconflict%252Dhit%2520Manipur%2520on%2520Wednesday.%5C%22%3Eanother%20incident%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20four%20Meitei%20villagers%20who%20had%20gone%20out%20to%20collect%20wood%20were%20allegedly%20shot%20by%20Kuki%20armed%20men%20after%20venturing%20into%20a%20forest%20along%20Bishnupur%20and%20Churachandpur%20districts%20on%20January%2010%20(Wednesday).%20The%20Manipur%20police%20confirmed%20the%20deaths%20on%20January%2011.%20One%20person%20was%20missing%2C%20and%20the%20search%20for%20him%20is%20still%20ongoing%2C%20according%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20a%20press%20note%20issued%20by%20Manipur%20police%2C%20the%20deceased%20were%20identified%20as%20Ibomcha%20Singh%20(51)%20and%20his%20son%20Anand%20Singh%20(20)%2C%20Romen%20Singh%20(38)%2C%20and%20Ahanthem%20Dara%20(56).%20Their%20bodies%20were%20found%20near%20Haotak%20Phailen.%20The%20search%20for%20Ahanthem%20Dara%20is%20still%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20attempted%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20both%20civil%20society%20organisations%20%3Cem%3E(%3C%2Fem%3ECSOs)%20of%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20community%20to%20inquire%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20dialogue%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAthouba%2C%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%2C%20a%20civil%20society%20organisation%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20primary%20responsibility%20for%20quelling%20violence%20lies%20with%20state%20and%20central%20forces%2C%20necessitating%20the%20disarming%20and%20cessation%20of%20the%20two%20conflicting%20groups.%20Without%20this%20intervention%2C%20any%20attempt%20to%20restore%20peace%20becomes%20futile.%20The%20initiation%20of%20dialogue%20can%20only%20occur%20once%20the%20situation%20normalises%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20civilian-level%20resolution.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20consistently%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20take%20decisive%20action%2C%20which%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20falls%20short%20of%20satisfying%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20expectations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20ongoing%20dialogue%2C%20Athouba%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20central%20government%20has%20control%20over%20the%20state%20government.%20%5BUnion%20home%20minister%5D%20Amit%20Shah%20himself%20has%20often%20mentioned%20that%20hills%20will%20be%20taken%20care%20of%20by%20them.%20A%20security%20advisor%2C%20appointed%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20has%20also%20taken%20over%20the%20charge%20of%20unified%20command.%20So%2C%20we%20can%20assume%20that%20the%20security%20issues%20and%20law%20and%20order%20are%20being%20completely%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20Centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGinza%20Vuolzong%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Kuki%20Community%20ITLF%2C%20has%20a%20different%20perspective%20on%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20and%20killing%20of%20innocent%20people.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20condone%20the%20killing%2C%20but%20this%20is%20wartime%20in%20Manipur.%20Many%20innocent%20people%20have%20