0ProComfort%20head%20is%20another%20feature%20that%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20replace%20other%20grooming%20tools.%C2%A0%20pre-shave%20attachment%20that%20uses%20the%20shaver's%20sonic%20technology%20to%20gently%20exfoliate%20and%20lift%20beard%20hair.%20If%20you%20use%20a%20separate%20tool%20to%20prepare%20your%20beard%20before%20shave%2C%20this%20attachment%20can%20easily%20replace%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SmartCare%20Center%20isn't%20new%20to%20the%20Series%209%20Pro%2B%2C%20but%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20useful%20accessories.%20Not%20only%20is%20it%20a%20nice%20place%20to%20dock%20your%20shaver%20when%20it's%20not%20in%20use%2C%20but%20it%20also%20cleans%2C%20lubricates%2C%20dries%2C%20and%20charges%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20upgrade%20on%20the%20Series%209%20Pro%2B%20is%20the%20mobile%20charging%20PowerCase.%20It's%20another%20safe%20place%20to%20store%20your%20shaver%20and%20automatically%20charges%2C%20extending%20the%20battery%20life%20to%20up%20to%206%20weeks%20%E2%80%94%20or%20much%20longer%20if%20you%20don't%20shave%20frequently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3A%20Braun%20Series%207%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20braun%20series%207%207075cc%20floating%20in%20water.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e5e7187fee23d02026a4a38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBraun%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Braun%20Series%207%20can%20%26quot%3Bread%26quot%3B%20the%20density%20of%20your%20beard%2C%20automatically%20adjusting%20its%20power%20to%20give%20you%20the%20closest%20shave%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Braun%20Series%207%20(7085cc)%20replaces%20the%20older%20Braun%20Series%207%20(7895cc)%20as%20our%20top%20overall%20pick%20for%20the%20best%20electric%20razors%20because%20of%20its%20dependability%20and%20a%20few%20key%20improvements.%20Like%20the%20previous%20generation%2C%20the%20Series%207%20(7085cc)%20features%20Braun's%20AutoSense%20technology%2C%20which%20reads%20the%20density%20of%20your%20beard%20and%20automatically%20adjusts%20its%20power%20to%20provide%20a%20clean%20shave%20in%20one%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20improvement%20in%20the%20design%20is%20the%20new%20360%C2%B0%20Flex%20Head%20shaver%20that%20contours%20to%20the%20curves%20of%20your%20face%20and%20neck.%20The%20new%20Series%207%20(7085cc)%20feels%20effortless%2C%20even%20in%20hard-to-shave%20areas%20like%20your%20Adam's%20apple%20or%20jawline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20model%20(7085cc)%20also%20has%20a%20detachable%20trimmer%20that%20goes%20in%20place%20of%20the%20shaver%2C%20unlike%20the%20previous%20model%20(7895cc)%2C%20which%20featured%20a%20slide-out%20trimmer%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20device.%20With%20the%20new%20design%2C%20the%20trimmer%20tool%20is%20placed%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20device%20so%20you%20can%20see%20exactly%20what%20you're%20doing.%20If%20you're%20having%20difficulty%20visualizing%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20designs%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbraun-series-7-electric-shaver-review%23what-it%2527s-like-to-use%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esee%20the%20side-by-side%20comparison%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%2050%20minutes%20of%20continuous%20shave%20time%2C%20the%20Braun%20Series%207%20(7085cc)%C2%A0typically%20lasts%20three%20weeks%20on%20one%20charge%20%E2%80%94%20and%20when%20it%20does%20die%2C%20you%20can%20get%20enough%20battery%20power%20for%20a%20single%20shave%20with%20a%205-minute%20quick%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20previous%20models%2C%20the%20Series%207%20(7085cc)%20is%20also%20entirely%20waterproof%2C%20so%20you%20can%20bring%20it%20in%20the%20shower%2C%20use%20it%20with%20water%20and%20shaving%20cream%2C%20or%20rinse%20it%20off%20in%20the%20sink%20when%20you're%20done.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EAmir%20Ismael%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbraun-series-7-electric-shaver-review%5C%22%3EBraun%20Series%207%20electric%20shaver%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%207071cc%20is%20the%20same%20as%20the%207085cc%2C%20except%20it%20doesn't%20include%20extra-length%20guard%20attachments.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20high-end%3A%20Panasonic%20ARC6%20Electric%20Shaver%20ES-LS9A-K%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Panasonic%20ARC6%20Electric%20Shaver%20ES-LS9A-K%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1b99943bb77284b9ceae2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Panasonic%20ARC6%20Electric%20Shaver%20is%20arguably%20the%20most%20advanced%20and%20premium%20shaver%20on%20the%20market.%20Replacing%20the%20previous%20generation%20ARC5%2C%20the%20ARC6%20features%20massive%20improvements%20including%20a%20new%20head%20with%20six%20blades%20forged%20from%20high-grade%20Japanese%20stainless%20steel%20and%20a%20more%20powerful%20motor%20with%2084%2C000%20cross-cutting%20motions%20per%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20six%20blades%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0two%20finishing%20blades%20designed%20to%20cut%20hair%20at%20the%20base%2C%20two%20titanium-coated%20blades%20for%20long%20and%20thick%20stubble%2C%20and%20two%20lift%20blades%20to%20lift%20and%20cut%20hairs%20that%20lay%20flat%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Panasonic%20ARC6%20has%20more%20blades%20than%20any%20electric%20shaver%20I've%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20its%20premium%20blade%20design%2C%20the%20shaver%20head%20moves%20in%2022%20independent%20directions%20to%20ensure%20it%20stays%20contoured%20to%20your%20face%20and%20neck%20at%20all%20times.%20Its%20sophisticated%20design%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20limiting%20nicks%20and%20cuts%2C%20while%20delivering%20a%20close%20shave%20with%20one%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20beard%20doesn't%20grow%20incredibly%20fast%20or%20thick%20and%20I%20keep%20most%20of%20my%20facial%20hair%2C%20so%20I%20couldn't%20truly%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20benefit%20of%20having%20such%20a%20powerful%20shaver.%20The%20auto-sensing%20technology%20increases%20or%20decreases%20power%20based%20on%20the%20density%20of%20the%20hair%20it's%20cutting%2C%20so%20I%20likely%20didn't%20use%20the%20full%20capacity%20of%20the%20motor%2C%20but%20I%20can%20see%20the%20value%20for%20men%20who%20either%20have%20thick%20beards%20or%20shave%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ARC6%20has%20an%20ergonomic%20design%20for%20in-hand%20comfort%20and%20a%20sleek%20matte%20finish.%20When%20turned%20on%2C%20a%20large%20LED%20screen%20displays%20useful%20information%20like%20battery%20percentage.%20The%20back%20side%20of%20the%20shaver%20includes%20an%20attached%20trimmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20bundled%20with%20a%20dock%20station%20that%20cleans%2C%20sanitizes%2C%20dries%2C%20and%20charges%20the%20shaver%2C%20a%20travel%20case%2C%20cleaning%20brush%2C%20and%20lubricating%20oil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20just%20under%20%24500%2C%20the%20Panasonic%20ARC6%20is%20expensive%2C%20but%20it%20has%20the%20most%20blades%2C%20an%20incredibly%20powerful%20motor%2C%20comes%20with%20all%20the%20extras%20you%20need%20to%20maintain%20the%20device%2C%20and%20is%20engineered%20to%20perform%20with%20efficiency%20and%20precision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20rotary%20shaver%3A%20Philips%20Norelco%20S9000%20Prestige%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Philips%20Norelco%20S9000%20Prestige%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1ba0043bb77284b9ceb24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20prefer%20shavers%20with%20rotary-style%20blades%20instead%20of%20linear%20foil%20shavers%2C%20Philips%20Norelco's%20S9000%20Prestige%20is%20the%20most%20advanced%20option%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20rotary%20shavers%20typically%20all%20feature%20three%20circular%20shavers%2C%20the%20S9000%20Prestige%20packs%20a%20lot%20of%20performance%20in%20each%20one.%20In%20total%2C%20there%20are%2072%20self-sharpening%20blades%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20cut%20hair%20in%20any%20direction.%20The%20exterior%20of%20the%20rotary%20blades%20is%20designed%20to%20lift%20the%20hair%2C%20before%20the%20blades%20cut%20as%20close%20to%20the%20skin%20as%20possible.%20And%20with%20165%2C000%20cutting%20actions%20per%20minute%2C%20you%20can%20achieve%20a%20close%20shave%20in%20just%20one%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S9000%20Prestige%20does%20a%20great%20job%20at%20cutting%20hair%2C%20but%20it%20also%20prioritizes%20protecting%20the%20skin.%20The%20shaver%20head%20features%20up%20to%20500%2C000%20hydrophilic%20microbeads%20to%20help%20the%20device%20glide%20across%20your%20skin.%20By%20limiting%20snags%2C%20you'll%20experience%20less%20irritation%20after%20you%20shave.%20Much%20like%20most%20premium%20shavers%2C%20the%20S9000%20Prestige%20has%20automatic%20beard-sensing%20technology%2C%20but%20I%20like%20that%20you%20can%20also%20manually%20adjust%20it%20using%20the%20%2B%20and%20-%20buttons%20on%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeaturing%20Philips%20Norelco's%20Ultraflex%20Suspension%20system%2C%20the%20S9000%20Prestige%20has%20one%20of%20the%20most%20comfortable%20contouring%20technology%20I've%20tested%2C%20which%20is%20incredibly%20important%20for%20clean%20shaves.%20With%20the%20orientation%20of%20rotary%20shavers%2C%20the%20S9000%20Prestige%20isn't%20good%20at%20shaving%20specific%20areas%20like%20below%20a%20beard%20line%20in%20the%20same%20way%20a%20foil%20shaver%20would.%20However%2C%20it%20comes%20bundled%20with%20a%20trimmer%20attachment.%20Rather%20than%20being%20built%20into%20the%20shaver%