20manipulate%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20dating%2C%20most%20people%20try%20to%20avoid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F11-warning-signs-you-are-dating-a-narcissist-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efalling%20for%20a%20narcissist%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20personality%20type%20some%20psychologists%20deem%20even%20harder%20to%20spot%3A%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdark-empath-traits-manipulation-pointed-jokes-charm-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edark%20empath%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20%26quot%3Bdark%20empath%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0191886920303615%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewas%20coined%20by%20researchers%20in%202021%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20describe%20people%20who%20rank%20high%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdark-triad-vs-light-triad-personality-traits-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edark%20triad%20personality%20traits%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20narcissism%2C%20psychopathy%2C%20and%20Machiavellianism%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20high%20in%20empathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Suzanne%20Degges-White%2C%20a%20licensed%20counselor%20and%20professor%20at%20Northern%20Illinois%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20dark%20empaths%20are%20like%20narcissists%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20except%20they%20can%20be%20even%20harder%20to%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20having%20empathy%20is%20%26quot%3Badding%20a%20tool%20to%20a%20narcissist%20toolbox%20that%20helps%20them%20be%20more%20effective%20in%20getting%20people%20to%20do%20what%20they%20want%20them%20to%20do%20or%20understanding%20how%20to%20appeal%20to%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20dark%20empath%20is%20a%20cluster%20of%20traits%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20diagnosis%20%E2%80%94%20Degges-White%20shared%20a%20few%20signs%20you%20might%20be%20entangled%20with%20a%20dark%20empath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20They%20express%20empathy%20but%20don't%20emotionally%20connect%20with%20you%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20name%20%26quot%3Bdark%20empath%26quot%3B%20implies%20the%20ability%20to%20care%20about%20other%20people%20on%20some%20level%2C%20Degges-White%20said%20there%20are%20different%20kinds%20of%20empathy%2C%20and%20not%20all%20of%20them%20translate%20to%20true%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCognitive%20empathy%20means%20'I%20understand%20on%20an%20intellectual%20level%20what%20you're%20feeling%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3B'You're%20crying%2C%20so%20you%20must%20be%20sad%3B%20you're%20looking%20distressed%2C%20so%20you%20must%20be%20having%20a%20hard%20time.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20between%20cognitive%20empathy%2C%20what%20dark%20empaths%20have%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fempathy-vs-sympathy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edeeper%20sense%20of%20empathy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20feel%20and%20bond%20over%20what%20the%20other%20person%20is%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20while%20a%20dark%20empath%20can%20take%20in%20the%20cues%20and%20details%20of%20a%20person's%20emotions%2C%20they%20never%20let%20those%20feelings%20personally%20affect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20They're%20extremely%20good%20at%20love%20bombing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Flove-bomb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELove%20bombing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20when%20a%20person%20showers%20you%20with%20affection%2C%20usually%20at%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20a%20relationship%20and%20any%20time%20they%20want%20to%20keep%20you%20around%20after%20a%20big%20fight%20or%20conflict.%20It's%20a%20common%20trait%20of%20narcissistic%20personality%20types%2C%20and%20can%20be%20even%20trickier%20to%20spot%20with%20dark%20empaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20they're%20what%20you%20want%20them%20to%20be%20because%20they%20can%20read%20what%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20Degges-White%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20classic%20narcissist%20might%20try%20to%20impress%20you%20with%20luxury%20gifts%20and%20expensive%20outings%2C%20a%20dark%20empath%20can%20take%20it%20a%20step%20further%20and%20try%20to%20mold%20themselves%20to%20your%20emotional%20needs%2C%20such%20as%20appearing%20more%20sensitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20trying%20to%20be%20that%20person%20because%20they%20want%20you%20to%20like%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20feeds%20their%20narcissistic%20ego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20They%20perfectly%20align%20with%20your%20political%20views%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20way%20dark%20empaths%20can%20try%20to%20impress%20others%20is%20by%20taking%20up%20all%20the%20same%20interests%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20dedication%20to%20the%20same%20political%20and%20social%20justice%20causes%2C%20Degges-White%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20we're%20fighting%20the%20common%20enemy%2C%20our%20emotions%20are%20revved%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Degges-White%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20dark%20empath%20would%20be%20very%20appealing%20because%20we'd%20be%20presuming%20that%20they%20share%20our%20interest%20and%20are%20as%20excited%20as%20we%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDegges-White%20said%20that%20because%20these%20people%20often%20lack%20impulse%20control%2C%20a%20dark%20empath%20%26quot%3Bmight%20be%20willing%20to%20even%20go%20more%20all%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20convincing%20others%20that%20they're%20a%20true%20crusader%20for%20the%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20They%20have%20narcissistic%20tendencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20their%20approach%20to%20winning%20you%20over%20might%20look%20different%20than%20classic%20narcissists%2C%20Degges-White%20said%20they%20ultimately%20treat%20you%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%20wearing%20you%20down%20in%20arguments%20and%20needing%20to%20be%20the%20center%20of%20attention%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20constantly%20feed%20their%20ego%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20either%20going%20to%20be%20walking%20with%20eggshells%20all%20the%20time%2C%20or%20you%20have%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20be%20their%20possession%20that%20they're%20able%20to%20trot%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20They%20rarely%20try%20to%20improve%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20not%20impossible%20for%20a%20dark%20empath%20to%20seek%20out%20self-improvement%2C%20Degges-White%20said%20it's%20quite%20rare%20and%20usually%20takes%20a%20dramatic%20life%20event%20to%20get%20them%20into%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20got%20to%20be%20a%20strong%20enough%20motivating%20factor%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20It%20could%20take%20the%20threat%20of%20prison%2C%20losing%20significant%20relationships%2C%20or%20a%20beloved%20job%20on%20the%20line%20for%20them%20to%20consider%20changing%20their%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20dated%20or%20known%20someone%20like%20this%3F%20Email%20the%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajpugachevsky%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejpugachevsky%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-dating-dark-empath-narcissism-empathy-relationships-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705098782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a0