rael%20urged%20the%20ICJ%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%20as%20groundless%20and%20reject%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20request%20to%20order%20a%20halt%20to%20the%20offensive%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-counter-genocide-accusations-world-court-2024-01-12%2F%5C%22%3Eas%20reported%20by%20Reuters.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fshaw-south-africa-cherry-picked-comments-by-israeli-politicians%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20lawyer%20Malcolm%20Shaw%20as%20saying%20that%20South%20Africa%20presented%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdistorted%20picture%E2%80%9D%20of%20comments%20made%20by%20Israeli%20politicians%20on%20the%20war%20in%20order%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%98genocidal%20intent%E2%80%99%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20produce%20random%20quotes%20which%20are%20not%20in%20conformity%20with%20government%20policy%20is%20misleading%20at%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-3%5C%22%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20South%20Africa%20told%20the%20top%20UN%20court%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20aerial%20and%20ground%20offensive%20%E2%80%93%20which%20killed%20almost%2024%2C000%20people%2C%20according%20to%20Gaza%20health%20authorities%20%E2%80%93%20aimed%20to%20bring%20about%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20destruction%20of%20the%20population%E2%80%9D%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-4%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20Israel%20rejected%20these%20accusations%2C%20saying%20it%20respected%20international%20law%20and%20had%20a%20right%20to%20defend%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2024%2F1%2F12%2Flive-israels-response-to-south-africas-genocide-case-at-the-icj%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Galit%20Raguan%2C%20acting%20director%20of%20the%20inter