ation%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22If%20Congress%20is%20%E2%80%98Anti-Hindu%E2%80%99%2C%20Are%20Shankaracharyas%20Also%20%E2%80%98Anti-Hindu%E2%80%99%3F%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12193806%2Fimage-1732.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ever%20since%20the%20Congress%20has%20declined%20its%20invitation%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%2C%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20left%20no%20opportunity%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fbjp-calls-congress-anti-hindu-for-declining-ram-temple-consecration-invite-2843222%5C%22%3Edeclare%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20as%20%E2%80%98anti-Hindu%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98anti-Ram%E2%80%99.%20The%20Congress%20has%20categorically%20termed%20the%20ceremony%20as%20one%20that%20is%20being%20turned%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbreaking-congress-declines-invitation-to-ram-temple-inauguration-calls-its-clearly-an-rss-bjp-event%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%2FRSS%20event%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20said%20that%20religion%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98personal%20matter%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20has%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20a%20political%20project%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20response%20is%20consistent%20with%20its%20opposition%20to%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20by%20Hindutva%20forces.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20being%20built%20atop%20the%20dome%20of%20the%20mosque%20is%20reason%20enough%20for%20all%20democratic-minded%20citizens%20who%20believe%20that%20Hindutva%20politics%2C%20since%20the%201990s%2C%20has%20expanded%20itself%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20the%20grave%20injustice%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%20to%20reach%20where%20it%20is%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20is%20not%20merely%20any%20temple.%20It%20is%20a%20temple%20where%20once%20a%20mosque%20stood%20and%20was%20brought%20down%20with%20sheer%20force%20of%20hate%20and%20muscle.%20It%20was%20an%20episode%20of%20national%20shame%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20which%20is%20being%20carried%20by%20the%20secular%20parties%20even%20today.%20The%20BJP%20has%20choreographed%20so%20much%20hype%20and%20hoopla%20to%20strip%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20of%20its%20history.%20It%20sees%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20as%20epochal%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20history%2C%20but%20wants%20everyone%20to%20conveniently%20forget%20about%20the%20violence%20that%20eventually%20led%20to%20its%20creation.%20For%20this%20precise%20reason%2C%20it%20has%20done%20everything%20on%20its%20part%20to%20wipe%20out%20any%20memory%20of%20its%20own%20violent%20history%20and%20the%20role%20that%20it%20played%20in%20sharply%20polarising%20India%20along%20religious%20lines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20would%20have%20wished%20that%20the%20opposition%20parties%20would%20have%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20remind%20people%20that%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20is%20not%20one%20based%20on%20faith%20but%20is%20a%20mere%20instrument%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20perpetuate%20a%20majoritarian%20common%20sense.%20Barring%20the%20Left%20parties%2C%20none%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20have%20taken%20such%20a%20stance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20non-attendance%20has%20given%20secular-minded%20citizens%20something%20to%20hold%20on%20to.%20More%20than%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20four%20Shankaracharyas%2C%20the%20foremost%20flag%20bearers%20of%20the%20Hindu%20faith%2C%20to%20give%20the%20event%20a%20miss%2C%20has%20certainly%20exposed%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20scheme%20to%20play%20around%20with%20people%E2%80%99s%20faith.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%204%20Highest%20Gurus%20of%20Sanatan%20Hindu%20Dharma%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Participate%20in%20Ram%20Temple%20Pran%20Pratistha%2C%E2%80%99%20Explains%20Pro-Hindutva%20Portal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20amplified%20the%20boycott%20by%20the%20Shankaracharyas%2C%20and%20questioned%20the%20BJP%20on%20why%20it%20is%20in%20a%20hurry%20to%20perform%20a%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20an%20incomplete%20temple.%20The%20Shankaracharyas%20believe%20that%20the%20Hindu%20Shastras%20do%20not%20permit%20anyone%20to%20perform%20consecration%20of%20a%20deity%20in%20an%20incomplete%20temple.%20They%20also%20believe%20that%20January%2022%20falls%20in%20the%20lunar%20month%20of%20Paus%2C%20which%20is%20inauspicious%20for%20the%20ceremony%2C%20while%20also%20claiming%20that%20the%20ceremony%20is%20being%20conducted%20in%20haste%20to%20hand%20political%20and%20electoral%20gains%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Are%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20also%20%E2%80%9Canti-Hindu%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-Ram%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20BJP%20should%20answer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20evident%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20using%20the%20ceremony%20for%20political%20gains%2C%20and%20precisely%20that%20is%20what%20the%20saffron%20party%20wants%20people%20to%20ignore%20by%20manufacturing%20a%20mass%20hysteria%20around%20the%20ceremony.%20A%20pliant%20media%2C%20as%20usual%2C%20has%20only%20aided%20and%20abetted%20the%20goal%20for%20the%20BJP.%20It%20has%20failed%20to%20question%20the%20BJP%2C%20even%20minutely%2C%20on%20how%20the%20political%20celebration%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20its%20ministers%20of%20the%20ceremony%20is%20not%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20promises%20a%20clear%20separation%20of%20religion%20and%20the%20State.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20the%20grand%20inauguration%20ceremony%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20presiding%20over%20it%20himself%2C%20is%20the%20biggest%20instance%20of%20how%20the%20BJP%20has%20successfully%20merged%20religious%20matters%20with%20State%20policy.%20With%20the%20blatant%20campaigning%20around%20welcoming%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20the%20temple%20by%20all%20the%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20from%20top%20to%20bottom%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20simultaneous%20announcement%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fayodhya-pm-narendra-modi-ayodhya-railway-station-airport-inauguration-ayodhya-dham-2482149-2023-12-30%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20worth%20Rs%2031%2C000%20crore%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20new%20airport%20and%20railway%20facility%20in%20the%20town%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20doubt%20about%20how%20the%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20milk%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20divisive%20politics%20to%20dive%20India%20even%20further.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20all%20the%20canvassing%20by%20the%20BJP%20against%20the%20Congress%20for%20allegedly%20being%20%E2%80%9Canti-Hindu%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20have%20decided%20to%20not%20visit%20Ayodhya%20(for%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPran%20Pratishtha%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Ram%20Temple).%20But%20there%20is%20no%20outrage%20over%20this.%20Does%20this%20not%20hurt%20religion%3F%20It%20is%20absolutely%20wrong%20to%20do%20politics%20over%20religious%20rituals.%20We%20are%20not%20declining%20a%20visit%20(to%20Ayodhya).%20We%20are%20not%20going%20to%20the%20January%2022%20event%20in%20Ayodhya%20that%20is%20being%20held%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20the%20RSS%20chief.%20Shankaracharyas%20are%20not%20going%20to%20that%20event%20either.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20disgusting%20politics%20that%20is%20being%20done%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Pawan%20Khera%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20event%20is%20religious%2C%20then%20is%20it%20happening%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20of%20the%20four%20Peeths%3F%20All%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20have%20said%20clearly%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPran%20Pratishtha%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20an%20incomplete%20temple%20cannot%20be%20done.%20If%20this%20event%20is%20not%20religious%2C%20then%20it%20is%20political%E2%80%A6%20It%20is%20not%20acceptable%20that%20the%20people%20of%20a%20political%20party%20are%20sitting%20as%20middlemen%20between%20me%20and%20my%20God%E2%80%A6%20A%20political%20group%20is%20acting%20like%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ethekedar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%A6%20Which%20%E2%80%98Panchang%E2%80%99%20has%20the%20BJP%20referred%20to%20before%20finalising%20the%20date%3F%20The%20date%20has%20been%20chosen%20keeping%20the%20elections%20in%20mind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20even%20before%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20the%20ceremony%20was%20being%20planned%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20project%2C%20wherein%20the%20attempted%20appropriation%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20to%20advance%20its%20Hindu%20supremacist%20politics%20was%20writ%20large.%20Contrary%20to%20what%20the%20opposition%20parties%20may%20think%2C%20common%20people%20who%20are%20not%20affiliated%20to%20any%20political%20party%20are%20wise%20enough%20to%20see%20the%20blatant%20politicking%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffor-the-bjp-the-hindu-card-is-no-longer-as-potent-as-it-once-was%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Card%20Is%20No%20Longer%20as%20Potent%20as%20It%20Once%20Was%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20certain%20sections%20in%20the%20Congress%20which%20are%20not%20convinced%20about%20the%20Congress%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20boycott%20the%20event.%20They%20believe%20that%20they%20may%20have%20a%20tough%20time%20explaining%20the%20party%20logic%20to%20people%20while%20canvassing.%20Many%20of%20them%20have%20also%20questioned%20the%20party%20leadership%20on%20the%20decision%20and%20have%20requested%20it%20to%20reconsider.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20perhaps%20the%20time%20when%20the%20leadership%20could%20also%20rein%20in%20and%20reorient%20the%20Congress%20towards%20taking%20ethical%20positions%20which%20are%20consistent%20with%20its%20party%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegional%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20and%20many%20others%2C%20including%20the%20right-wing%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray)%20group%20had%20already%20called%20out%20the%20political%20instrumentalisation%20of%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony.%20The%20Congress%20has%20come%20in%20late%20but%20now%20should%20stick%20to%20it%20with%20aggression.%20This%20is%20the%20time%20for%20the%20party%20to%20forcefully%20represent%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20original%20liberal-democratic%20idea%20of%20India.%20Only%20then%2C%20it%20can%20retain%20its%20relevance%20in%20the%20times%20of%20a%20majoritarian%20onslaught%2C%20and%20not%20by%20capitulating%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20a%20manufactured%20mass%20hysteria.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705069802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%