cal%20processes%2F%20rituals%2C%20as%20laid%20out%2C%20for%20example%2C%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESkand%20Purana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFailing%20such%20due%20observances%20authorised%20and%20executed%20by%20enshrined%20religious%20heads%2C%20the%20seer%20has%20cautioned%20that%20the%20idol%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20over%20by%20undesirable%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%2C%20mocking%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20gestures%20that%20habitually%20accompany%20his%20victory%20public%20addresses%2C%20asked%20whether%20he%20(the%20seer)%20is%20expected%20to%20sit%20and%20clap%20while%20Modi%20fronts%20the%20consecration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20seer%20has%20underscored%20the%20unflattering%20point%20that%20the%20event%20is%20merely%20a%20public%20relations%20show%20aimed%20at%20lifting%20the%20electoral%20prospects%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20the%20question%20must%20be%20asked%3A%20who%20is%20more%20proximate%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESanata%20Dharma%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20seer%20of%20Puri%20or%20the%20executive%20head%20of%20the%20constitutional%20republic%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%204%20Highest%20Gurus%20of%20Sanatan%20Hindu%20Dharma%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Participate%20in%20Ram%20Temple%20Pranpratistha%2C%E2%80%99%20Explains%20Pro-Hindutva%20Portal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20if%20the%20Congress%20is%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20wrong%20for%20not%20attending%20the%20ceremony%20scheduled%20for%20January%2022%2C%20why%20not%20also%20the%20Shakaracharya%20of%20Puri%2C%20who%20has%20also%20declined%20to%20be%20present%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlternately%2C%20why%20is%20the%20Sangh%20fighting%20shy%20of%20engaging%20the%20Shankaracharya%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShastrartha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20or%20scholarly%20debate%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20hallowed%20traditions%20of%20the%20Sanatan%2C%20so%20that%20lay%20Hindus%20might%20better%20understand%20the%20intricacies%20of%20the%20issue%20at%20hand%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20now%2C%20it%20does%20seem%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20closer%20to%20the%20Sanatan%20position%20than%20those%20who%20are%20so%20relentlessly%20propagating%20the%20Sanatan%20character%20of%20the%20event%20to%20come.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20would%20it%20not%20be%20apposite%20for%20media%20houses%20to%20foreground%20the%20historic%20nature%20of%20the%20schism%20here%20between%20the%20Shankaracharya%20and%20the%20forces%20of%20political%20Hinduism%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20which%20side%20may%20the%20nationalist%20corporates%20be%20on%20who%20now%20elbow%20the%20said%20media%20channels%20in%20establishment%20directions%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it%20does%20seem%20to%20be%20the%20case%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20little%20reason%20to%20cower%2C%20given%20that%20its%20reservations%20have%20been%20so%20openly%20and%20authoritatively%20endorsed%20by%20the%20highest%20religious%20supremo%20among%20the%20Sanatan%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20messaging%20wherewithal%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20the%20resources%20to%20match%20the%20onslaught%20of%20the%20official%20armoury.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20thereby%20hangs%20an%20unlovely%20tale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%