%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaghavan%E2%80%99s%20brand%20of%20nothing-is-what-it-seems%20stories%20plant%20a%20doubt%20in%20the%20viewer%2C%20keeping%20us%20on%20our%20toes%2C%20forcing%20us%20to%20ask%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20Kaif%E2%80%99s%20face%20really%20conveying%3F%20Can%20we%20trust%20her%20affected%20delivery%2C%20when%20she%20talks%20about%20her%20drug-abuser%20husband%2C%20who%20is%20paranoid%20about%20her%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20then%20that%20the%20essence%20of%20this%20unusual%20collaboration%20dawns%20on%20us%20%E2%80%93%20why%20Raghavan%20went%20with%20Kaif.%20It%E2%80%99s%20precisely%20because%20Kaif%E2%80%99s%20face%20is%20hard%20to%20read%20that%20it%20lends%20itself%20superbly%20to%20the%20cipher%20that%20her%20character%2C%20Maria%2C%20is.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FUUKdUNMgk7Q%3Fsi%3DQp0sHlempvPAV4E2%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20meet%20her%20at%20a%20busy%20Colaba%20restaurant%20with%20her%20daughter%2C%20Annie%2C%20where%20she%20has%20been%20stood%20up%20by%20a%20date.%20Maria%20aces%20the%20look%20of%C2%A0%20a%20hapless%2C%20young%20mother%20forced%20to%20spend%20Christmas%20eve%20by%20herself.%20Bumping%20into%20%E2%80%9CDubai-return%E2%80%9D%20Albert%20(Vijay%20Sethupathi)%20at%20the%20eatery%2C%20the%20mother-daughter%20meet%20him%20again%20inside%20a%20movie%20theatre%20at%20Regal%20showing%20%3Cem%3EPinocchio.%3C%2Fem%3E%20As%20a%20show%20of%20courtesy%2C%20Albert%20offers%20to%20drop%20them%20home%20%E2%80%93%20which%2C%20she%20assures%2C%20is%20a%20couple%20of%20lanes%20away.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20strangers%2C%20accompanied%20by%20a%20little%20girl%20and%20a%20giant%20teddy%20bear%2C%20make%20their%20way%20to%20Maria%E2%80%99s%20residence%20on%20Christmas%20eve.%20She%20offers%20him%20a%20drink%2C%20puts%20Annie%20to%20bed%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20soon%20exchanging%20their%20life%20stories.%20They%20discover%20how%20they%E2%80%99ve%20both%20loved%20and%20lost.%20She%20suggests%20they%20go%20out%20for%20a%20walk.%20An%20Arijit%20Singh%20ballad%20plays%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20build-up%20for%20Sriram%20Raghavan%20is%20elaborate%2C%20and%20to%20his%20credit%2C%20not%20rushed.%20We%20know%20this%20is%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true%2C%20and%20Raghavan%20knows%20we%20know%20this.%20So%2C%20he%20deliberately%20makes%20us%20invest%20in%20this%20bizarre%20pairing%20%E2%80%93%20a%20diva%20from%20Hindi%20cinema%2C%20and%20the%20working-class%20hero%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20who%20has%20burst%20into%20superstardom%20only%20relatively%20recently.%20Their%20different%20dialects%2C%20backgrounds%2C%20acting%20energies%20%E2%80%93%20everything%20seems%20to%20contradict%20each%20other.%20Only%20until%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKaif%E2%80%99s%20laboured%20dialogue%20delivery%20unmasks%20the%20performance%20within%20the%20performance.%20Sethupathi%E2%80%99s%20loose%20body%20language%2C%20firms%20up%20when%20the%20time%20comes.%20The%20Richard%20Linklater%20rom-com%20version%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMerry%20Christmas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20where%20two%20strangers%20falling%20in%20love%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20night%2C%20makes%20way%20for%20the%20Sriram%20Raghavan%20noir%20we%20all%20came%20to%20see.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20corpse%20is%20discovered.%20People%20come%20clean%20about%20their%20past.%20The%20%E2%80%98love%20story%E2%80%99%20is%20derailed%2C%20but%20is%20it%20really%3F%20It%20would%20be%20unfair%20to%20reveal%20anything%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20an%20hour%20into%20the%20141-minute%20film%2C%20is%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMerry%20Christmas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20truly%20begins.%20Characters%20go%20their%20different%20ways%2C%20new%20characters%20bump%20into%20them%20and%20the%20entire%20premise%20comes%20together.%20In%20typical%20Raghavan%20fashion%2C%20the%20film%20starts%20with%20a%20split-screen%20shot%20of%20hands%20grinding%20tablets%2C%20and%20another%20set%20of%20hands%20making%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epodi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20masala%20and%20hiding%20a%20ring%20in%20it.%20As%20the%20film%20goes%20on%2C%20both%20scenes%20fill%20the%20necessary%20blanks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKaif%20is%20committed%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20and%20is%20serviceable%20for%20the%20film.%20It%E2%80%99s%20Sethupathi%2C%20who%20towers%20over%20the%20film%20with%20his%20easy%2C%20assured%20presence.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20left%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20unfinished%20in%20life%2C%20but%20never%20a%20bottle%20of%20chilled%20beer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks%20at%20one%20point.%20Raghavan%20laces%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20with%20a%20wild%20supporting%20cast%20including%20Sanjay%20Kapoor%2C%20Tinu%20Anand%2C%20Vinay%20Pathak%2C%20Ashwini%20Kalsekar%2C%20Pratima%20Kannan%20and%20Radhika%20Apte.%20It%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20second%20hour%20that%20Raghavan%E2%80%99s%20filmmaking%20really%20gets%20down%20to%20business%2C%20staging%20weirdly%20comical%20scenes%2C%20which%20we%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20expect.%20No%20one%20is%20who%20they%20say%20they%20are%2C%20everyone%20is%20lying%20to%20some%20degree.%20In%20a%20situation%20like%20this%2C%20who%20do%20you%20really%20trust%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMerry%20Christmas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20nowhere%20as%20dense%20or%20convoluted%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAndhadhun%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2018)%2C%20but%20does%20that%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20step%20down%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20simple%2C%20relatively%20contained%20premise%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20bears%20all%20the%20dazzling%20technique%20of%20a%20Raghavan%20film.%20The%20detailing%20in%20the%20production%20design%20is%20fantastic%2C%20the%20music%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20Pritam%E2%80%99s%20ballads%20and%20a%20mix%20of%20Christmas%20hymns%2C%20Western%20orchestra%20and%20vintage%20Hindi%20film%20music%20(the%20film%20pays%20tribute%20to%20Shakti%20Samanta).%20Raghavan%20also%20makes%20sure%20to%20include%20his%20love%20for%20food%20and%20alcohol%2C%20with%20a%20scene%20featuring%20Albert%20making%20dosas%2C%20and%20multiple%20characters%20gulping%20their%20drinks%20in%20more%20than%20one%20scene.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20litmus%20test%20of%20Raghavan%E2%80%99s%20story%20lies%20in%20the%20final%20moments%2C%20when%20the%20audience%20becomes%20privy%20to%20the%20guilty%20party%2C%20and%20the%20thrill%20is%20will%20they%20get%20away%3F%20Raghavan%20drowns%20all%20the%20dialogue%20with%20a%20piece%20Western%20classical%20music%20as%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20final%20reveal%20takes%20place%2C%20and%20all%20hell%20breaks%20loose.%20This%20is%20someone%20at%20the%20height%20of%20his%20mastery%2C%20able%20to%20get%20to%20the%20essence%20of%20a%20scene%20best%20among%20his%20contemporaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20might%20critique%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20initial%20staging%20portions%2C%20for%20how%20long%20Raghavan%20takes.%20If%20you%20ask%20me%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMerry%20Chritsmas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20feature-film%20sized%20flex%20by%20one%20of%20Hindi%20cinema%E2%80%99s%20most%20masterful%20filmmakers.%20We%E2%80%99re%20watching%20someone%20at%20his%20most%20assured.%20He%20takes%20his%20time%2C%20because%20he%20can.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705066221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12184354%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ff