tory%20of%20targeted%20attacks%2C%E2%80%9D%20Beg%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CAny%20compromise%20in%20security%20measures%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mehbooba%20survived%20the%20accident%20without%20injuries%2C%20her%20personal%20security%20officer%20and%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20SUV%20car%2C%20a%20black%20Mahindra%20Scorpio%2C%20which%20collided%20with%20a%20private%20car%20near%20the%20Sangam%20area%20of%20south%20Kashmir%2C%20suffered%20injuries.%20Both%20the%20victims%20are%20out%20of%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMehboob%20Beg%20expresses%20concern%20over%20%E2%80%98security%20lapse%E2%80%99%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMehboobaMufti%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MehboobaMufti%3C%2Fa%3E%20road%20mishap%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5LRg6QRFwP%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5LRg6QRFwP%3C%2Fa%3E%20via%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMehboobbeg%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Mehboobbeg%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20J%26amp%3BK%20PDP%20(%40jkpdp)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjkpdp%2Fstatus%2F1745754830994293227%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThe%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3EWire%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Ereached%C2%A0out%20to%20the%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20M.K.%20Sinha%2C%20for%20his%20comment%20on%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20PDP.%20Sinha%20oversees%20the%20security%20arrangements%20for%20protected%20persons%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%C2%A0but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20a%20police%20spokesperson%20rejected%20the%C2%A0PDP%E2%80%99s%20allegations%2C%20saying%20that%20Mehbooba%20enjoys%20%E2%80%9Cextensive%20and%20sophisticated%20security%20arrangement%C2%A0(sic)%20designed%20to%20ensure%20her%20safety%20at%20all%20times%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20out%20details%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20her%20security%20detail%20comprises%2034%20personnel%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmultiple%20vehicles%2C%20including%20a%20vehicle-mounted%20jammer%20to%20neutralize%20electronic%20threats.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20accident%2C%20Beg%20had%20said%20that%20the%20administration%C2%A0%E2%80%9Ctook%20an%20hour%E2%80%9D%20to%20arrange%20an%20alternative%20vehicle%20for%20the%20PDP%20chief%2C%20even%20though%20a%20second%20car%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20her%20cavalcade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CZ%2B%20security%20protocols%20typically%20include%20an%20optional%20car%20in%20the%20escort%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20was%20not%20there%2C%20indicating%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20lapse%20in%20(security)%20preparedness%20that%20cannot%20be%20overlooked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20compromised%20security%20detail%20for%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20not%20only%20jeopardises%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20individual%20but%20also%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20broader%20commitment%20to%20ensuring%20the%20security%20and%20stability%20of%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20Beg%20said%2C%20while%20urging%20the%20administration%20to%20%E2%80%9Csafeguard%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20leaders%20who%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20sociopolitical%20fabric%20of%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20police%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cswift%20response%20post-accident%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20%E2%80%9Calternative%20vehicle%20was%20deployed%20within%20an%20hour%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20the%20accident%20happened%20at%20Bijbehara%20which%20is%20at%20a%20distance%20of%20approximately%2050%20kms%20from%20Srinagar%20from%20where%20the%20Special%20BP%20vehicle%20was%20dispatched.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIdeally%20security%20arrangements%20of%20senior%20protected%20persons%20are%20not%20discussed%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20become%20necessary%20to%20reassure%20our%20protectees%2C%20including%20party%20functionaries%20of%20PDP%2C%20that%20the%20security%20arrangements%20for%20Ms.%20Mufti%20were%20and%20continues%C2%A0(sic)%20to%20be%20very%20much%20in%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20PDP%20has%20accused%20the%20administration%20of%20overlooking%20the%20security%20of%20Mehbooba%2C%20who%20was%20unceremoniously%20toppled%20as%20the%20last%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20state%20in%202018%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20coalition%20government%20with%C2%A0the%20PDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20had%20served%20a%20notice%20to%20Mehbooba%2C%20asking%20her%20to%20vacate%20the%20Fairview%20Residence%20on%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20upscale%20Gupkar%20Road%2C%20where%20she%20had%20been%20living%20since%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20committee%2C%20in%20a%20report%2C%C2%A0had%20recommended%20that%2010%20guard%20posts%2C%20five%20watch%20towers%2C%20one%20wireless%20grid%2C%20two%20access%20control%20units%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctwo%20Detts%E2%80%9D%20be%20built%20for%20securing%20the%20Khimber%20house.%20However%2C%20a%20PDP%20leader%20said%20that%20no%20follow-up%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20administration%20on%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20however%C2%A0sought%20to%20downplay%20the%20issue%2C%20%E2%80%9CHer%20residence%20at%20Khimber%20is%20guarded%20by%20a%20strong%20contingent%20of%20paramilitary%20guard%20personnel%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20a%20security%20review%20carried%2