n%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%E2%80%99s%20reports%20then.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20the%20ED%20naming%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20daughters%20in%20its%20chargesheet%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20spokesperson%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Manoj%20Jha%20said%20to%20the%20media%20in%20Delhi%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ED%20is%20doing%20this%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20two%20persons%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20power%20structure%20to%20trouble%20their%20political%20opponents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20fictitious%20case%20in%20which%20several%20FIRs%20were%20filed%20in%202008%2C%20and%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20ED%20closed%20them%20in%202011%20after%20finding%20no%20evidence.%20The%20investigating%20agencies%20reopened%20it%20suddenly%20in%202021-22%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Lotus%E2%80%99%20that%20worked%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20boomeranged%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20chargesheet%20in%20a%20special%20PMLA%20court%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20January%209%20is%20a%20clear-cut%20example%20of%20political%20vendetta.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJha%20cited%20how%20the%20leaders%20of%20Delhi%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%20%E2%80%93%20all%20non-BJP%20ruled%20states%20%E2%80%93%20were%20being%20targeted%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI.%20He%20apprehended%20that%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20may%20heap%20more%20trumped-up%20charges%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20rivals%20ahead%20of%20January%2022%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMedia%20focus%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mainstream%20media%20%E2%80%93%20print%20and%20electronic%20%E2%80%93%20largely%20downplayed%20or%20ignored%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20statements.%3C%2Fs