nfrastructure%20has%20been%20relegated%20to%20the%20periphery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20(who%20are%20now%20also%20known%20as%20leaders%20of%20INDIA)%20are%20not%20unnerved%20by%20the%20developments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20we%20are%20anxious.%20The%20BJP%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20has%20let%20loose%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20to%20trouble%20Lalu%2C%20Tejashwi%20and%20others%20who%20are%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20will%20not%20be%20cowed%20down.%20We%20will%20take%20the%20battle%20to%20the%20court%20of%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENalin%20Verma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705064411000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29183927%2FThe-Wire-23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funnerved-by-ed-cbi-action-ahead-of-ayodhya-but-wont-be-cowed-down-rjds-manoj-jha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20investigative%20agencies%20continue%20to%20issue%20summons%20to%20leaders%20opposed%20to%20Hindutva%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20RSS%20and%20the%20Hindi%20media%20remain%20focused%20on%20the%20Ram%20Temple%E2%80%99s%20January%2022%20consecration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funnerved-by-ed-cbi-action-ahead-of-ayodhya-but-wont-be-cowed-down-rjds-manoj-jha%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%