%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335433%2Fnorthstar-school-rajkot-sustainable-design-santiniketan-open-learning-ib-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echild%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Lal%20looks%20back%20on%20his%20journey%20being%20filled%20with%20miracles%20he%20never%20anticipated.%20Resilience%2C%20he%20says%20has%20been%20his%20best%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20fateful%20day%20in%202001%20when%20Satyarthi%20was%20conducting%20a%20rally%20in%20his%20village%20%E2%80%94%20an%20education%20march%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Bachpan%20Bachao%20Andolan%20(Save%20Childhood%20Movement)%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Lal%20says%20Satyarthi%20spotted%20him%20carrying%20heavy%20boulders.%20A%20short%20conversation%20later%2C%20Satyarthi%20had%20convinced%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20parents%20that%20their%20child%20was%20meant%20for%20greater%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fchild-labour-1704799800.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amar%20Lal%20with%20the%20children%20from%20the%20ashram%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fchild-labour-1704799800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fchild-labour-1704799800-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fchild-labour-1704799800-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fchild-labour-1704799800-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fchild-labour-1704799800-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337821%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmar%